      • getInstance

        public static MetaEvaluator getInstance()
        Factory method. You should not override this class to add more of your own evaluators. Just get the instance and addEvaluator(AbstractFunctionEvaluator) to it. It will snoop through your evaluator too. If you are writing your own evaluator, start your type numbers should be negative.
